**11 May / Jet Brawley - New Update**

__**New Update 11 May 2021**__

- New Features
 - New Commands 
- Turned 90%+ Commands Into Non-Case-sensitive
- Bug Fixes 

__**New Feature ( Server Vote Tracker )**__

To Learn More About This Command, Run `-help tracker`. 

__**New Commands**__

`-calc <MATH>` - Calculate Something 
`-bug` - To Report Any Bug

If You Notice Any Bug , Please Report To Us By Running `-bug` Command And Follow The Instruction Given, and so we can take action as soon as possible :cpu:  :slight_smile:
